1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 31=

3
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:27,760
Yunchang,

4
00:00:30,090 --> 00:00:31,399
are you really getting married?

5
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:34,280
Who are you?

6
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:36,079
How dare you trespass in Shen Manor!

7
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:38,720
The Gate Bureau is here
catching a thief.

8
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:40,320
- What's going on?
- What's happening?

9
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,200
Insolence!

10
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:54,012
(Harmonious and Gentle)
How dare you resist official officers?

11
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:55,640
Who are you trying to arrest?

12
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:57,640
Her.

13
00:01:02,119 --> 00:01:03,240
She is my daughter-in-law.

14
00:01:03,719 --> 00:01:04,719
What if I don't allow it?

15
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,799
Then, I'll take you down,

16
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:09,560
too.

17
00:01:11,879 --> 00:01:13,079
Young lady,

18
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,319
you're young, but you talk big.

19
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,680
Do you know that in all of Xichuan,

20
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,760
(Happiness. Bright Moon and Clear Winds)
no one dares to disrespect me?

21
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:21,980
No matter how great the Shen family is,

22
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,640
do you dare to be
an enemy of the Gate Bureau?

23
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:25,599
Young lady,

24
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:29,799
if you dare to be an enemy
of all the Xichuan outlaws,

25
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,239
then bring it on.

26
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,280
I'll be waiting.

27
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,400
Fine.

28
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,680
I will take everyone in this manor

29
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,760
into custody.

30
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:43,560
I'm afraid you don't have the ability.

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,879
No one move!

32
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:54,799
(Token)
I have the royal command token of the Prince of Shu.

33
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:56,000
By order of the Prince of Shu.

34
00:01:58,330 --> 00:01:59,840
Here's the Prince of Shu's oral decree.

35
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:03,599
Shen Gongquan once saved my life.

36
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:06,560
No one is allowed
to act presumptuously in his manor.

37
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:07,581
(Token)
The order concluded.

38
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:16,800
Young lady,

39
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,439
do you still want to fight?

40
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,360
I never thought

41
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:26,520
the current Prince of Shu
would act as your guarantor.

42
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,439
In my younger days,
I traveled the martial world.

43
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:33,120
By chance, I saved the Prince's life.

44
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,560
The Prince was grateful,

45
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:38,159
ensuring no one in Xichuan
would dare to touch the Shen family.

46
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,990
The Prince of Shu
is the current Emperor's uncle.

47
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,960
Let's drop it for today.

48
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,199
Fine.

49
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,660
Since the Prince of Shu
has given orders,

50
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:55,319
the Gate Bureau will comply.

51
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:57,680
Chu Yunchang,

52
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,680
you'd better hide in Xichuan
for the rest of your life.

53
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,639
Otherwise,

54
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:04,759
once you leave
the protection of the Shen family,

55
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:07,360
I will make sure you
have no place to be buried!

56
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,439
Withdraw!

57
00:03:13,525 --> 00:03:18,662
(Shen Manor)

58
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:21,390
Sooner or later,
I'll have Grandfather wipe this place out.

59
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,400
Yu,

60
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,400
where is Chief Mao?

61
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,350
Deputy Luo,

62
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,639
what are you doing now?

63
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,919
Chief Mao is inside.

64
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,790
I'm going to find him.

65
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,080
Deputy Luo,

66
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:36,000
you've just arrived in Chengdu
and almost caused a major incident.

67
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,520
Fortunately, no violent
conflict broke out today,

68
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:41,039
otherwise, how would
I explain it to the Prince of Shu?

69
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:43,039
And now you want to go back?

70
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,520
If you really push
Shen Gongquan too far,

71
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,990
I'm afraid neither of us
will be able to handle the consequences.

72
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,840
But Yu is still inside.

73
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:51,560
Deputy Luo,

74
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,599
calm down.

75
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,439
He'll be fine.

76
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,439
Are you really going to marry him?

77
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:07,520
Yes.

78
00:04:11,610 --> 00:04:12,970
I just want to ask you one thing.

79
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,079
Are you being forced,

80
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,240
or is it of your own free will?

81
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,120
Of my own free will.

82
00:04:24,462 --> 00:04:27,987
♪Can't bear to keep acting anymore♪

83
00:04:28,512 --> 00:04:31,575
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

84
00:04:32,462 --> 00:04:36,037
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

85
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,720
Fine.

86
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:42,240
Today is my wedding day.

87
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,240
Chief Mao,

88
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,720
please

89
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,600
leave.

90
00:04:53,037 --> 00:04:53,797
Did you hear that?

91
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,319
My wife told you to leave.

92
00:04:56,475 --> 00:05:00,275
♪Despite countless ordeals♪

93
00:05:00,525 --> 00:05:04,637
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

94
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,560
Leave now!

95
00:05:07,112 --> 00:05:09,120
Wait, man, who are you?

96
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,439
Right, leave now!

97
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:11,959
Go!

98
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:15,839
Leave quickly! Go!

99
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,439
Fine.

100
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,240
Hurry, let's go.

101
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:19,920
I'm leaving.

102
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,759
- Go back.
- Go.

103
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,360
Go back.

104
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,199
- Hurry and leave.
- Just go.

105
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:22,759
I'm leaving.

106
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,439
Get going.

107
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:28,462
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

108
00:05:28,537 --> 00:05:32,275
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

109
00:05:32,487 --> 00:05:36,337
♪Lies and vows,
let them stay in the past♪

110
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,160
Chu Yunchang.

111
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,720
From now on,

112
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,199
we are finished.

113
00:05:56,437 --> 00:06:00,225
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

114
00:06:00,325 --> 00:06:04,250
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

115
00:06:04,462 --> 00:06:08,675
♪Lies and vows,
let them stay in the past♪

116
00:06:08,725 --> 00:06:15,700
♪Let's return to when we first met♪

117
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:18,262
(Happiness)

118
00:06:18,437 --> 00:06:19,396
I am terribly sorry.

119
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,800
My deepest apologies.

120
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,000
The mood was briefly dampened just now,

121
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,680
but everything is back to normal.

122
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,920
The couple may
continue with the ceremony.

123
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,120
Wait!

124
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:30,399
Feng?

125
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:34,279
Feng,

126
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,759
what are you doing here?

127
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,079
(Shen Liefeng, Young Master of the Shen family)
Liefeng, why did you come out?

128
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:37,639
I...

129
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,600
What do you want to say?

130
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,439
I... I don't...

131
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,319
Could it be that you want to perform
the wedding bows yourself?

132
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:47,600
No, I don't want to marry her.

133
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,639
What nonsense is that?

134
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,639
Feng,

135
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,360
I am doing this for your own good.

136
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,879
It's all for the sake of the Shen family.

137
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,519
No, I...

138
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:57,040
Did she say something to you?

139
00:06:59,770 --> 00:07:01,319
What could I possibly have said to him?

140
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,720
Lord Shen,

141
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,079
it seems you don't understand

142
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,510
Young Master Shen's feelings at all.

143
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,079
His feelings?

144
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,040
Father,

145
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,720
all these years,

146
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,959
could it be you didn't know

147
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:16,399
that my heart
already belongs to someone else?

148
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,959
I do not love Sect Leader Chu.

149
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:24,319
Your heart belongs to someone?

150
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,839
Who is it?

151
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,319
She is

152
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,600
Biyao, who has always taken care of me.

153
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,680
Hurry, let's go.

154
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,079
Young Master,

155
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:45,335
(Biyao, Shen family maid)
let me help you.

156
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:48,160
I've been tormented by illness
in my whole life.

157
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,800
Only when I am with Biyao

158
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,800
do I forget
all the troubles of this world.

159
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:58,000
I cannot live my life without her.

160
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,199
Therefore,

161
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,240
I will never take
Chu Yunchang as my wife.

162
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,319
Biyao, come.

163
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,360
Come.

164
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,800
You... You two...

165
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,560
Biyao, tell the truth.

166
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,639
Are you and my brother in love?

167
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:22,639
Lord Shen,

168
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,800
I deserve to die,

169
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,199
but I

170
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,199
truly love the Young Master.

171
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:27,800
Ridiculous!

172
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:31,240
You lowly servant, how dare you
have feelings for your master?

173
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,400
Do you know what you've done?

174
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,159
Father,

175
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,240
I also truly love Biyao.

176
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,919
Silence!

177
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:39,200
How... How dare you two do such a thing?

178
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:40,360
Why wouldn't they?

179
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,990
Biyao has always
taken care of Young Master Shen

180
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,960
with such devotion and care.

181
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:47,120
Spending every day together,

182
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,300
feelings were bound to grow.

183
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,759
Why try to stop them?

184
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,500
They are not of equal social standing.

185
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:52,559
This is improper!

186
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,559
Lord Shen,

187
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,320
that's where you're wrong.

188
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:58,279
We in the martial world
have never cared for such trifles.

189
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:01,440
Your son and Biyao
are in love with each other.

190
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,840
So why are you so furious?

191
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,000
Indeed, Lord Shen.

192
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,879
Do you have the heart to watch your son

193
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,440
marry a woman he doesn't love

194
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,930
and be miserable
for the rest of his life?

195
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:14,000
Father, I felt that I was
a burden to the Shen family

196
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,399
and brought shame to you.

197
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,399
So I never dared
to leave the back courtyard,

198
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:19,720
let alone defy your wishes.

199
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,159
But now,

200
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,559
since it concerns
Biyao's and my happiness,

201
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,879
I'm emboldened

202
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,799
to ask for your blessing, Father.

203
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,200
Their love is unbreakable.

204
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,879
I withdraw voluntarily.

205
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:37,039
Father, Liefeng has suffered
his whole life.

206
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,399
This is his only wish.

207
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,520
Please just grant it to him.

208
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:40,919
You...

209
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,759
You have made me

210
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:46,320
lose face completely
before the heroes of Xichuan!

211
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,279
Father,

212
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,639
please just give
Biyao and me your blessing.

213
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:50,919
As long as I'm alive,

214
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,200
don't even think about it!

215
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:54,559
Then, I will wander
the world with Biyao!

216
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,919
I'm leaving too!

217
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,159
Don't you dare!

218
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,360
Lord Shen,

219
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:05,080
why are you being so stubborn?

220
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,200
My family affairs

221
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,240
are none of your business.

222
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:11,000
Well, this happened at my wedding.

223
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:15,360
I know you're angry right now,

224
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:17,159
but think about it carefully.

225
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:19,360
Isn't children's happiness

226
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:21,759
what parents value most?

227
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,000
Because of Mr. Shen's illness,

228
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,120
you

229
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,759
want to carry on the family line.

230
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:30,162
But Biyao

231
00:10:30,162 --> 00:10:32,002
can also carry on the Shen family line.

232
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:33,879
Besides,

233
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:35,600
don't you still have Die?

234
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,480
Though Die is a woman,

235
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,879
she is ten times better than any man.

236
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,440
I'm a woman too,

237
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:47,000
but I'm also the Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect,

238
00:10:47,010 --> 00:10:48,400
a Grandmaster of the martial world.

239
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,559
Why insist on a male successor?

240
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,440
Die is also your successor.

241
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,240
Father,

242
00:10:57,919 --> 00:10:59,720
please bless Liefeng and Biyao.

243
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,700
As for revitalizing the Shen family,

244
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,440
I will take full responsibility.

245
00:11:07,110 --> 00:11:08,159
- Young Master.
- Liefeng.

246
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:11,039
I have no other wish in this life.

247
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:13,159
Please, Father, grant it.

248
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,360
Fellow heroes,

249
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:29,039
I am very sorry.

250
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:31,799
Today's wedding is temporarily canceled.

251
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,480
I shall choose another auspicious day

252
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,000
for my son, Liefeng,

253
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,440
to marry Biyao.

254
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:41,559
Good!

255
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,399
Young Master...

256
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,919
Congratulations!

257
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,080
- Congratulations, Young Lord!
- Congratulations!

258
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,639
That's wonderful.

259
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,679
Yes, indeed.

260
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:53,559
I also have another announcement today.

261
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:56,200
From now on, my family estate

262
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:59,159
will be inherited by my daughter, Yidie.

263
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:01,840
Father.

264
00:12:03,399 --> 00:12:04,399
My daughter, Yidie,

265
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,279
has assisted me since childhood.

266
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,120
She has mastered all my skills.

267
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:10,720
In the future,
all matters of the Shen family

268
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:13,519
will be decided by my daughter, Yidie.

269
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:16,480
Good!

270
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,080
Father,

271
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:19,000
you've finally recognized me.

272
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,679
Congratulations.

273
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,519
Die,

274
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,720
all these years,

275
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:25,200
I've treated you unfairly.

276
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:29,799
Congratulations, Lord Shen.

277
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,440
Congratulations, Miss Shen.

278
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:33,200
Congratulations, Miss Shen.

279
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,960
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

280
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,120
Congratulations!

281
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:37,759
Great news!

282
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,720
- Good!
- Excellent!

283
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,399
What a double celebration!

284
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:43,279
A great joy!

285
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:44,559
Congratulations!

286
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,279
Si,

287
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:58,279
you rest for a bit.

288
00:12:58,425 --> 00:12:58,945
Yes.

289
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:00,720
Wushuang.

290
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,840
Yu, are you okay?

291
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,399
You scared me to death.

292
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:19,919
Master, you're finally awake.

293
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:20,960
You really worried us.

294
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:23,639
Look, I've even got
dark circles under my eyes.

295
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,559
Where are we going?

296
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,390
We're going back to the Gate Bureau.

297
00:13:28,737 --> 00:13:29,537
The Gate Bureau.

298
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:31,759
What about Yunchang?

299
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:32,759
She...

300
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:36,120
She's already married to Shen Liefeng.

301
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,690
She has the Prince of Shu's protection.

302
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,180
We can only wait for her
to leave before capturing her.

303
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,919
Did she really marry Shen Liefeng?

304
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,360
Yu,

305
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,519
don't be heartbroken.

306
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,840
It should be in that direction.

307
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,559
I didn't expect Shen Gongquan
to actually be a man of his word.

308
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:17,080
He really gave us
Dongfang Bai's hiding place.

309
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,960
If he hadn't spoken up,
who would have thought that Dongfang Bai

310
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,790
was hiding right here
on Skyscraper Cliff?

311
00:14:23,039 --> 00:14:23,840
You know,

312
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,240
on the wedding day,

313
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,720
I was really worried for you.

314
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,679
Tell me,

315
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,080
did you already know Shen Liefeng

316
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,559
was in love with Biyao?

317
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:34,159
Was that why you agreed to the wedding?

318
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:36,360
To provoke him on purpose?

319
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,679
The first time
I saw Shen Liefeng and Biyao,

320
00:14:39,679 --> 00:14:41,679
I realized they were in love.

321
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:43,399
Shen Liefeng
was held back by his illness,

322
00:14:43,399 --> 00:14:44,600
and Biyao by her status,

323
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,039
so neither of them spoke out.

324
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:48,060
I deliberately agreed to the marriage,

325
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,320
believing Shen Liefeng

326
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,440
would call it off for Biyao's sake.

327
00:14:52,679 --> 00:14:54,080
So you had it all calculated.

328
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,600
You really had us worried sick.

329
00:14:57,240 --> 00:15:00,120
I'm sure you noticed it long ago, Uncle.

330
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,320
Seeing how confident you looked,

331
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,559
you must have had a counter-strategy.

332
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,360
It's just that...

333
00:15:07,279 --> 00:15:08,440
Mao Buyu...

334
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,039
Don't bring up sensitive subjects.

335
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:16,720
I only care about the truth now.

336
00:15:17,159 --> 00:15:18,080
As for everything else,

337
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,720
we'll talk about it later.

338
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,200
Enough talk. Let's get moving.

339
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,399
Alright, let's go.

340
00:15:37,519 --> 00:15:38,200
Slow down, Yu.

341
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,519
Master, how are you feeling?

342
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,080
I'm fine.

343
00:15:43,399 --> 00:15:44,039
Yu.

344
00:15:44,537 --> 00:15:45,137
Shun.

345
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,200
Are you okay?

346
00:15:51,287 --> 00:15:55,062
(Skyscraper Cliff Thatched Hut)

347
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:58,375
(Skyscraper Cliff Thatched Hut)

348
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,879
Is anyone here?

349
00:16:00,012 --> 00:16:01,440
(Skyscraper Cliff Thatched Hut)

350
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,360
Is anyone here?

351
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,320
Is anyone here?

352
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:57,120
How can these scarecrows be alive?

353
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,200
Darn it.

354
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:17,370
These scarecrows
aren't afraid of weapons at all.

355
00:17:20,839 --> 00:17:22,519
How can these scarecrows have life?

356
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:27,570
Someone must
be controlling them in secret.

357
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:50,990
These scarecrows
are controlled by golden threads.

358
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,599
Cut them!

359
00:18:03,079 --> 00:18:03,680
Pull!

360
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,680
That fall nearly killed me.

361
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:15,599
He's the one
manipulating the scarecrows.

362
00:18:15,759 --> 00:18:16,799
Who on earth are you?

363
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:18,480
(Powder-Faced Buddha, Dongfang Bai)
I am their master.

364
00:18:18,839 --> 00:18:19,720
And who are you?

365
00:18:20,319 --> 00:18:21,680
So you are Dongfang Bai?

366
00:18:28,487 --> 00:18:31,762
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

367
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:34,675
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

368
00:18:35,175 --> 00:18:40,893
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

369
00:18:42,075 --> 00:18:45,395
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

370
00:18:45,525 --> 00:18:48,445
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

371
00:18:49,613 --> 00:18:54,853
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

372
00:18:56,075 --> 00:18:58,468
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

373
00:18:58,468 --> 00:19:02,118
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

374
00:19:02,187 --> 00:19:05,677
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

375
00:19:05,775 --> 00:19:08,750
♪To the ends of time♪

376
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:12,125
♪The moon traces your face♪

377
00:19:12,312 --> 00:19:15,900
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

378
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:22,140
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

379
00:19:22,475 --> 00:19:25,690
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

380
00:19:25,975 --> 00:19:29,513
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

381
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:32,825
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

382
00:19:32,825 --> 00:19:35,925
♪On our way to forever♪

383
00:19:35,925 --> 00:19:39,775
♪The moon traces your face♪

384
00:19:39,775 --> 00:19:43,135
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

385
00:19:43,325 --> 00:19:49,285
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

386
00:19:50,362 --> 00:20:00,002
♪Just to be with you♪
